Description:
Notice Serial Number:  P JB030322/01-34   312333683
You have failed to ensure that the electrical consumer unit installed within Unit 5, marked as J D, is of such construction to prevent, so far as is reasonably practicable, danger in that there was access to live electrical systems via holes in the top and right side of the box.

Notice Serial Number:  P JB030322/02-34  312334036 
You have failed to ensure that the electrical socket to the left of the roller shutter door into Unit 5 is of such construction or suitably protected as to prevent, so far as is reasonably practicable, danger arising from exposure to live electrical components

Notice Serial Number:  P JB 030322/03-34   312334049
You have failed to ensure that the electrical socket on the left wall of Unit 5 is of such construction or suitably protected as to prevent, so far as is reasonably practicable, danger arising from exposure to live electrical components

Notice Serial Number:  P JB030322/04-34   312334079
You have failed to ensure that the electrical system supplying the MIG Welder L405 in Unit 5 is constructed in such a way to prevent danger, so far as is reasonably practicable, in that the sheath is not complete, allowing access to exposed electrical cable,

Notice Serial Number:  P JB030322/05-34   312334089
You have failed to ensure that the electrical connectors on the floor of unit 6 are constructed in such a way to prevent danger, so far as reasonably practicable, in that the sheath to the electrical connector is not complete allowing access to exposed electrical components
